    <p>This is where Rishte Hi Rishte can help you. Rishte Hi Rishte is an elite match-making service for High Net Worth Individuals across the world. It is by invitation only and caters to only serious clients. It was founded in 1976 with only the passion for bringing people together. Over more than 40 years, Rishte Hi Rishte has become the preferred choice of around the world, looking for love and their soul mate. Rishte Hi Rishte is where matrimonial dreams find their perfect match.</p>

<p>We understand the doubts and skepticism that someone may face before meeting a potential match. Our key objective is to provide a personal touch to our clients, so we act more like family members than just a protocol-bound matrimonial firm Therefore, our team work on your profile, shortlist profiles, arrange meetings, everything and provides special attention to every individual client, screening each profile carefully, matching interests and expectations of potential matches to generate only the most suitable options for you. As a result of our special attention to detail and understanding of individual needs, Rishte Hi Rishte has a database of thousands of profiles and a long list of success stories.</p>

<p>The services that Rishte Hi Rishte provides work on a systematic structure which ensures that your potential matches are of the same level as you in terms of their education, background, refinement and success. It is this method that leaves little room for a mismatch. For this reason, Rishte Hi Rishte reserves the right to not accept a client if they are not found to be serious or unfit for the structure in which the service is provided. Rishte Hi Rishte services are not dominated by only the superficial. It is about understanding each individual to their heart and soul, what keeps them going, what makes them succeed, their fears and doubts, their joys and successes, everything and then bring them closer to someone who can understand and share their life. It is about bringing people closer to the love they deserve.</p>

<p>We don’t guarantee a marriage with our services; what we do guarantee is generating the most suitable and compatible potential matches for you. The company’s main motto is that finding true love for people is a noble venture and so we don’t entertain people who are not completely serious.
